  "texts": [
    "Research Question 3 regards the influence of the temperature setting on the LLMs' scores.",
    "Overall, on average, a temperature of 0.7 provided slightly higher scores (mean = 10.72) on both tests than a temperature of 0.0 (mean = 10.06).",
    "The difference was just over 1 point for the quantitative ability test (mean difference = 1.04).",
    "And the difference was small for the verbal ability test (mean difference = 0.26).",
    "Thus, a non-zero temperature provided small improvements in test performance."
